These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, lemonade, hot-chocolate, cola, milk, iced-tea
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, american, pakistani, polish, indonesian, russian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, rugby, volleyball, badminton, weightlifting, skiing, snowboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, boat, skateboard, trike, tram, helicopter, motorbike
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the pakistani##1
 3. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the colombian is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the japanese is on the right of the russian##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the polish##1
 8. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the motorbike and the indonesian##2
 9. the polish is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the taxi##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the american##1
14. the indonesian is the person driving the skateboard##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the russian##1
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
17. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the american##1
18. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the polish##1
19. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | milk        | cola | lemonade      | hot-chocolate     | water      | iced-tea     |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani         | russian   | japanese | indonesian    | polish | american |
